After spending an off-season and a year of lock-down on his home trails in Santa Cruz, California, @r_doggystyles, aka Ryan Howard, finally flew the coop to visit a friend and check out their riding scene. With the right mix of features, banter, wildflowers, and local insight to lead the way, any place can become your next epic destination. Watch R-Dog x Beacon Hill, WA now!⁣
⁣
Video By: @mindsparkcinema / @isaacwallenn #RockShox

node.text:
To kick off our Brains Behind the Brand series, we introduce you to Jesse Jakomait, a Senior Design Engineer who has been part of the RockShox team for 11 years. Jesse's love for bikes is amplified by an engineering degree and superhuman mindset that has pushed him to set records and stand on more peaks than anyone we know. World, meet Jesse.⁣
⁣
Video By: @joeyschusler #RockShox

node.title: Brains Behind the Brand: Jesse Jakomait

node.text:
Embodying the spirit of slopestyle mountain biking, @brandonsemenuk shows his creativity in his latest edit REALM. Designing four unique features, Brandon continues to push boundaries and challenge what is possible.⁣
⁣
"Like any mountain bike trail or course, you work with the given terrain to make the best features imaginable. In this situation, we knew we wanted to create a course that would ride well top to bottom, but also offer up some opportunities for creativity along the way."⁣
⁣
With the @redbullbike Joyride 10-year anniversary on the near horizon, fans can vote for their favorite feature to be included at Joyride. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Head to our Stories to enter @brandonsemenuk's REALM. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Video By: @revel_co / @redbullbike #RockShox

The Enduro World Series delivered yet another exciting round of tight racing in both the Men's and Women's fields. @isabeau_c found her groove with consistent results in all six stages, leading her to her second gold of her season.⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Having the advantage of winning the Prologue on Saturday, @jackmoir_ came out of the gates chomping at the bit for another win. With three stage wins in Round 6 and two race wins in the past week, Jack continues to pull ahead in the Overall ranking.⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Keeping his bronze streak up, @kevin.miquel sent two for two this weekend claiming the third podium spot. Stay tuned as athletes head to Crans-Montana, Switzerland on September 11-12 for Round 7 of @world_enduro. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Photos By: @maddogboris / @svenmartinphoto #RockShox

node.text:
New to the @world_enduro circuit is not one, but two stops in Loudenvielle, France. With stages starting above treeline, riders dropped into some of the steepest, fast and loose descents they have seen thus far this season in Round 5 today.⁣
 ⁣
Hungry for the gold, @jackmoir_ ended the day with three stage wins and a 12-second lead, clutching the Overall Series ranking. 23-seconds behind Jack was @kevin.miquel in 3rd place. Frenchman @cecce_camoin had the best finish of his season, winning the U21 Men's category.⁣
 ⁣
The new venue was no match for young @hatt1e_harnden. With a massive 20-second gap in the final stage, Hattie secured her second Elite Women’s win, proving she's not leaving the podium any time soon.⁣
 ⁣
Athletes have tomorrow to catch their breath before a Prologue stage on Saturday, giving them the chance to earn more points going into Round 6 on Sunday. ⁣⁣
 ⁣
Photos By: @svenmartinphoto / @mtbisokay #RockShox
